casebody.data:
In re Campbell.

[Cite as In re Campbell (2001), 91 Ohio St.3d 1202.]

(No. 00-1176 Submitted December 13, 2000 Decided January 31, 2001.) David K. Greer, for appellant Florence Campbell. Heather R. Saling, for appellee Franklin County Children Services. Paul Skendelas, for appellee guardian ad litem.

The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
